* ============================================================================
* SKY130 Bandgap Reference — TT Corner Model Library
* ============================================================================
*
* Extracted from: google/skywater-pdk-libs-sky130_fd_pr (Apache 2.0)
* Source:         https://github.com/google/skywater-pdk-libs-sky130_fd_pr
* Corner:         TT (typical-typical)
* Devices:        sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8  — 1.8V PMOS (BSIM4, 52-bin)
*                 sky130_fd_pr__pnp_05v5_W3p40L3p40  — 5V PNP BJT
*                 sky130_fd_pr__res_generic_po  — Poly resistor
*
* This is a MINIMAL extraction for bandgap reference simulation only.
* For full PDK usage, install the complete sky130_fd_pr library.
